Look closely at the Ultimate Universal Benefit chart for cat litter and allergy medicine. We have picked these two intentionally for their diversity. Note the ladder-like hierarchy as you scan from the bottom up. Also notice that the benefit example is more about the product at the bottom of the ladder and more about the target consumer at the top.
